OL,6,FThe scale of the problem at HMP
OL,7,FManchester, previously known as
OL,8,FStrangeways, included inmates burning
OL,9,Fholes in windows to receive drone
OL,10,Fdeliveries and prompted Mr Taylor to
OL,11,Flast year tell the Justice Secretary
OL,12,Fto put the prison into emergency
OL,13,Fmeasures.
