OL,3,CWatchdog warns of 'national security
OL,4,Cthreat' from drone drug drops to jails
OL,6,FMr Taylor said: "It is highly alarming
OL,7,Fthat the police and prison service
OL,8,Fhave in effect ceded the airspace
OL,9,Fabove two high-security prisons to
OL,10,Forganised crime gangs which are able
OL,11,Fto deliver contraband to jails holding
OL,12,Fextremely dangerous prisoners,
OL,13,Fincluding some who have been
OL,14,Fdesignated as high-risk category A.
OL,16,F"The safety of staff, prisoners and
OL,17,Fultimately that of the public is
OL,18,Fseriously compromised by the failure
OL,19,Fto tackle what has become a threat to
OL,20,Fnational security.
