OL,3,CWatchdog warns of 'national security
OL,4,Cthreat' from drone drug drops to jails
OL,6,F"The prison service, the police and
OL,7,Fother security services must urgently
OL,8,Fconfront organised gang activity and
OL,9,Freduce the supply of drugs and other
OL,10,Fillicit items which so clearly
OL,11,Fundermine every aspect of prison life."
OL,13,FThe Ministry of Justice (MoJ) promised
OL,14,Fimprovements including a crackdown on
OL,15,Fdrugs after Mr Taylor found there to
OL,16,Fbe "catastrophic levels" present at
OL,17,Fthe category B prison in Manchester
OL,18,Fwhich can hold more than 700 men,
OL,19,Fincluding a handful of the "most
OL,20,Fdisruptive" and high-risk prisoners
OL,21,Funder close supervision.
