OL,6,F"The number of weapons and other
OL,7,Fillicit items found in recent months
OL,8,Fwas among the highest of all prisons
OL,9,Fholding adult men and the proportion
OL,10,Fof prisoners testing positive for drug
OL,11,Fuse was very high at 39%," the report
OL,12,Fsaid.
OL,14,FMeanwhile, the findings on Long Lartin
OL,15,Ftold of drones carrying "large
OL,16,Fpayloads of illicit items" into the
OL,17,Fcategory A Worcestershire prison.
