OL,6,FHolding almost 600 inmates, including
OL,7,Fthose mainly serving life sentences
OL,8,Fand "some very dangerous men", the
OL,9,Fnumber of drugs and phones coming into
OL,10,Fthe jail was a "serious concern".
OL,12,FMore than 50% of prisoners told
OL,13,Finspectors it was "easy" to get drugs
OL,14,Fand alcohol, which the watchdog
OL,15,Fbranded an "astonishing rate" for a
OL,16,Fhigh-security jail, according to the
OL,17,Freport.
