OL,3,CWatchdog warns of 'national security
OL,4,Cthreat' from drone drug drops to jails
OL,6,FThe latest warning comes after Mr
OL,7,FTaylor likened another high-security
OL,8,Fjail, HMP Garth in Lancashire, to an
OL,9,F"airport" because there were so many
OL,10,Fdrones flying in drugs.
OL,12,FAnd a report from Independent
OL,13,FMonitoring Boards (IMB) ` made up of
OL,14,Fvolunteers tasked by ministers with
OL,15,Fscrutinising conditions in custody `
OL,16,Finto "crumbling" jails in England and
OL,17,FWales said delays in fixing broken
OL,18,Fprison windows was making it easier
OL,19,Ffor drones to be used to deliver drugs
OL,20,Fand weapons.
