OL,6,FIn December, MPs heard contraband was
OL,7,Fbeing taken into HMP Parc in South
OL,8,FWales in "children's nappies", while
OL,9,Fthere were "industrial specification
OL,10,Fdrone drops" from organised crime
OL,11,Fgangs.
OL,13,FAndrea Coomber, chief executive of the
OL,14,FHoward League for Penal Reform, said:
OL,15,F"These appalling inspection reports
OL,16,Fare a warning that problems in prisons
OL,17,Fspill out into the towns and cities
OL,18,Faround them.
