OL,3,CWatchdog warns of 'national security
OL,4,Cthreat' from drone drug drops to jails
OL,6,F"A system that has been asked to do
OL,7,Ftoo much, with too little, for too
OL,8,Flong is now so compromised as to
OL,9,Fbecome a threat to national security."
OL,11,FPia Sinha, chief executive of the
OL,12,FPrison Reform Trust, described the
OL,13,Finfiltration of criminal gangs in
OL,14,Fprisons as a "serious and worrying
OL,15,Fdevelopment", arguing giving more
OL,16,Fpower to governors to update security
OL,17,Fequipment and recruit staff as well as
OL,18,Ffocusing on rehabilitating inmates
OL,19,Fwould reduce demand for drugs.
